quran[4]{c,v,t,f}:
  112,4,"Ma jiro axad u dhigma (Alle oo la mid ah ama la barbar dhigo)."
  113,1,"Dheh: Waxaan ka magan galayaa Rabbiga oogga (dillaacsha, waa Alle'e),"
  113,2,"Sharka wuxuu abuuray;"
  113,3,"Iyo sharka habeenka mugdiga badan markuu mugdigiisa daboolo (samada iyo arlada dhexdooda)."